OL,5, Banks offering unjustifiably low       
OL,6, savings rates to their customers will  
OL,7, face "robust action", the UK's         
OL,8, financial watchdog has said.           
OL,10,FThe Financial Conduct Authority's (FCA)
OL,11,Fwarning came as part of a plan to      
OL,12,Fensure banks are passing on interest   
OL,13,Frate rises to savers.                  
OL,15,FUnder new rules that came into force on
OL,16,FMonday, banks must prove they are      
OL,17,Foffering their customers fair value.   
OL,19,FSeparately, a campaign to help those   
OL,20,Fstruggling with mortgages has started. 
